HEADWORD: Starter
<hw>Start"er</hw> <pr>(st⟦aum⟧rt"⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>One who, or that which, starts; <as>as, a
<ex>starter</ex> on a journey; the <ex>starter</ex> of a
race</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A dog that rouses game.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Startful</ent>⟦br⟧
